369
00:34:01,283 --> 00:34:02,573
<font color="yellow">Ini dia.</font>

370
00:34:02,573 --> 00:34:04,693
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kita datang ke sini?</font>

371
00:34:04,693 --> 00:34:06,814
<font color="yellow">Aku cuma minta kau memberitahuku
