00:34:26,113 --> 00:34:27,113
<font color="yellow">Astaga.</font>

377
00:34:29,524 --> 00:34:33,153
<font color="yellow">Biarawan Myung Chul.</font>

378
00:34:33,323 --> 00:34:37,914
<font color="yellow">Apa benda ini membantu sama sekali?/
