00:35:23,093 --> 00:35:26,403
<font color="yellow"><i> Bong Pal, kau! Bong Pal!</i></font>

388
00:35:26,403 --> 00:35:28,443
<font color="yellow"><i> Bong Pal!</i></font>

389
00:35:29,803 --> 00:35:32,024
<font color="yellow">Hapus? Sudah dihapus.</font>

