<font color="yellow">Yakin mau masuk?/
Ya. Tentu saja.</font>

397
00:35:58,803 --> 00:36:01,343
<font color="yellow">Aku harus masuk.
Aku harus masuk.</font>

398
00:36:04,564 --> 00:36:06,823
<font color="yellow">Kita harus minum ini dulu.</font>

399
00:36:30,463 --> 00:36:32,684
<font color="yellow">Sekarang, hari ini...</font>

400
00:36:32,684 --> 00:36:35,713
<font color="yellow">...kami akan menunggu
