403
00:36:40,983 --> 00:36:43,524
<font color="yellow">Dan pergi ke kamar mandi sekarang.</font>

404
00:36:43,524 --> 00:36:46,923
<font color="yellow">Kalian juga harus persiapkan mentalmu./
