00:37:14,173 --> 00:37:18,533
<font color="yellow">Kim Hyun Ji... Kim Hyun Ji...</font>

411
00:37:18,533 --> 00:37:21,283
<font color="yellow">Aku bukan sekolah disini.</font>

412
00:37:21,283 --> 00:37:23,573
<font color="yellow">Apa aku sekolah di sini?</font>

