00:37:32,874 --> 00:37:34,573
<font color="yellow">Aku disini!</font>

414
00:37:36,343 --> 00:37:38,354
<font color="yellow">Hantu!</font>

415
00:37:38,354 --> 00:37:40,264
<font color="yellow">Dia kembali lagi.</font>

416
00:37:40,264 --> 00:37:43,244
<font color="yellow">Suasana hatiku sedang buruk,
