425
00:39:35,684 --> 00:39:36,914
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

426
00:39:36,914 --> 00:39:40,394
<font color="yellow">Kau belum pernah ciuman?</font>

427
00:39:40,394 --> 00:39:43,213
