439
00:40:32,724 --> 00:40:36,064
<font color="yellow">Apa kameranya berfungsi dengan baik?</font>

440
00:40:45,383 --> 00:40:47,994
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak takut. Aku tidak takut.</font>

441
00:40:47,994 --> 00:40:50,794
<font color="yellow">Itu petir. Wah, itu petir.</font>

442
00:40:51,633 --> 00:40:53,733
<font color="yellow">Kukira apaan.</font>

443
00:40:56,483 --> 00:40:58,533
<font color="yellow">Lagi pula, aku akan tidur.</font>

444
00:40:58,533 --> 00:40:59,533
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.</font>

445
00:42:56,943 --> 00:42:59,783
<font color="yellow">Siapa bajingan itu?</font>

446
