462
00:46:18,434 --> 00:46:20,923
<font color="yellow">Kubilang pukul belakang kepalanya!</font>

463
00:46:40,644 --> 00:46:42,744
<font color="yellow">Kau lumayan juga.</font>

464
00:46:42,744 --> 00:46:44,584
<font color="yellow">Aku biasa-biasa saja kok.</font>

465
00:46:44,584 --> 00:46:47,573
<font color="yellow">Kau juga lumayan./
Tapi...</font>

466
00:46:47,923 --> 00:46:50,764
<font color="yellow">Siapa namamu?/
Hyun Ji. Kim Hyun Ji.</font>

467
00:46:50,764 --> 00:46:53,264
<font color="yellow">Dan kau?/
Aku?</font>

468
00:46:55,423 --> 00:46:57,383
<font color="yellow">Park Bong Pal.</font>

469
00:47:00,764 --> 00:47:03,003
<font color="yellow">Namamu Park Bong Pal?</font>

470
00:47:03,003 --> 00:47:05,914
<font color="yellow">Untunglah namamu tak terbalik.</font>

471
00:47:07,224 --> 00:47:09,343
<font color="yellow">Astaga...</font>

472
00:47:09,343 --> 00:47:11,463
<font color="yellow">Aku menangis.</font>

473
00:47:11,883 --> 00:47:13,934
<font color="yellow">Astaga, tapi...</font>

474
00:47:13,934 --> 00:47:16,894
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah menangkap hantunya,
