496
00:48:13,894 --> 00:48:15,664
<font color="yellow">Kau itu sangat lemah.</font>

497
00:48:17,024 --> 00:48:18,604
<font color="yellow">Terserahlah.</font>

498
00:48:18,604 --> 00:48:20,604
<font color="yellow">Apa yang akan kubicarakan denganmu?</font>

499
00:48:20,604 --> 00:48:22,613
<font color="yellow">Jangan muncul lagi.</font>

500
00:48:22,613 --> 00:48:24,713
<font color="yellow">Kalau tidak, kau akan mati di tanganku.</font>

501
00:48:24,713 --> 00:48:27,814
<font color="yellow">Coba saja.</font>

502
00:48:34,434 --> 00:48:36,343
<font color="yellow">Siapa disana?</font>

