508
00:49:02,573 --> 00:49:04,854
<font color="yellow">Kau bertarung dengan siapa hari ini?</font>

509
00:49:04,854 --> 00:49:07,443
<font color="yellow">Ada orang aneh ini...</font>

510
00:49:07,443 --> 00:49:10,294
<font color="yellow">Kau mungkin dikutuk. Orang seperti itu terus muncul dalam hidupmu.</font>

511
00:49:12,314 --> 00:49:18,244
<font color="yellow">Hyun Ji, kenapa bibirmu?</font>

512
00:49:20,383 --> 00:49:23,184
<font color="yellow">Aku baru saja menabrak sesuatu.</font>

