00:49:30,923 --> 00:49:32,974
<font color="yellow">Serius? Ingatan apa?</font>

516
00:49:32,974 --> 00:49:35,584
<font color="yellow">Ingatan apa?/
Ingatan...</font>

517
00:49:35,814 --> 00:49:38,704
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak ingat sekarang.
Bagaimana ini?</font>

